    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is priced to reflect its history as a hardworking daily driver. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some minor staining and wear on the driver's bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and aging suspension components. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable commuter who doesn't mind some cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections.",
