    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996 Turbo is a pristine specimen featuring the iconic Mezger 3.6L twin-turbocharged power plant. Engineered with a true dry-sump lubrication system and a reinforced crankcase, the engine provides unwavering oil pressure under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle to an all-wheel-drive system that remains tight and responsive. The suspension geometry is factory-perfect, with no compliance issues in the bushings or dampers. This vehicle exhibits zero thermal cycling wear on the cooling system and maintains exceptional compression across all cylinders. A collector-grade example for the discerning driver who values mechanical purity and peak performance.",
