      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in showroom condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a rainy day. The Jet Black Metallic paint is flawless, protected by a ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish without a single rock chip or swirl mark in sight. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' state; the black leather sport seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it still retains that factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the crisp Bose surround sound system to the PCM navigation, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized Porsche centers. The staggered 20-inch Carrera S wheels are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with ample tread. This is a collector-grade example that drives with the same precision and tightness as it did the day it left the dealership. Includes two keys, all original manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
